(57, 'Python While Loops', 'python-while-loops', '<h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 32px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Python Loops</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 1.2em; margin-bottom: 1.2em; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">Python has two primitive loop commands:</p><ul style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><span class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 15.75px; color: crimson; background-color: rgba(222, 222, 222, 0.3); padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px;\">while</span>&nbsp;loops</li><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><span class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 15.75px; color: crimson; background-color: rgba(222, 222, 222, 0.3); padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px;\">for</span>&nbsp;loops</li></ul><hr style=\"margin-right: -16px; margin-left: -16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 32px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">The while Loop</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 1.2em; margin-bottom: 1.2em; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">With the&nbsp;<span class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 15.75px; color: crimson; background-color: rgba(222, 222, 222, 0.3); padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px;\">while</span>&nbsp;loop we can execute a set of statements as long as a condition is true.</p><div class=\"w3-example\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(231, 233, 235); border-radius: 5px; padding: 8px 20px; margin: 24px -20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-shadow: none !important;\"><h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">Example<br></h3><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\">Print i as long as i is less than 6:</p><div class=\"w3-code notranslate pythonHigh\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; width: auto; background-color: rgb(21, 32, 43); color: white; padding: 8px 12px; border-left: 4px solid rgb(40, 44, 52); overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 16px !important; margin-bottom: 16px !important;\"><span class=\"pythoncolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: black;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">i =&nbsp;</span><span class=\"pythonnumbercolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\">1</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"pythonkeywordcolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">while</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;i &lt;&nbsp;</span><span class=\"pythonnumbercolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\">6</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">:</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"pythonnumbercolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class=\"pythonkeywordcolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">print</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">(i)</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"pythonnumbercolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;i +=&nbsp;</span><span class=\"pythonnumbercolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\">1</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><span class=\"pythonnumbercolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\"></span></span></div><a target=\"_blank\" class=\"w3-btn w3-margin-bottom\" href=\"/learn-python/56/try-it/demo_while\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(76, 175, 80); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: none; display: inline-block; padding: 6px 18px; vertical-align: middle; overflow: hidden; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; text-wrap: nowrap; user-select: none; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 17px; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 16px !important;\">Try it Yourself </a></div><div class=\"w3-panel w3-note\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 16px 32px; margin: 24px -32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 204); border-left: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;\">Note:</span>&nbsp;remember to increment i, or else the loop will continue forever.</p></div><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 1.2em; margin-bottom: 1.2em; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">The&nbsp;<span class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 15.75px; color: crimson; background-color: rgba(222, 222, 222, 0.3); padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px;\">while</span>&nbsp;loop requires relevant variables to be ready, in this example we need to define an indexing variable,&nbsp;<span class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 15.75px; color: crimson; background-color: rgba(222, 222, 222, 0.3); padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px;\">i</span>, which we set to 1.</p><hr style=\"margin-right: -16px; margin-left: -16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 32px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">The break Statement</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 1.2em; margin-bottom: 1.2em; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">With the&nbsp;<span class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 15.75px; color: crimson; background-color: rgba(222, 222, 222, 0.3); padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px;\">break</span>&nbsp;statement we can stop the loop even if the while condition is true:</p><div class=\"w3-example\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(231, 233, 235); border-radius: 5px; padding: 8px 20px; margin: 24px -20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-shadow: none !important;\"><h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">Example</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\">Exit the loop when i is 3:</p><div class=\"w3-code notranslate pythonHigh\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; width: auto; background-color: rgb(21, 32, 43); color: white; padding: 8px 12px; border-left: 4px solid rgb(40, 44, 52); overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 16px !important; margin-bottom: 16px !important;\">i =&nbsp;<span class=\"pythonnumbercolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\">1</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><span class=\"pythonkeywordcolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">while</span>&nbsp;i &lt;&nbsp;<span class=\"pythonnumbercolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\">6</span>:<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><span class=\"pythonnumbercolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\"></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"pythonkeywordcolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">print</span>(i)<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><span class=\"pythonnumbercolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\"></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"pythonkeywordcolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">if</span>&nbsp;i ==&nbsp;<span class=\"pythonnumbercolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\">3</span>:<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"pythonkeywordcolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">break</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;i +=&nbsp;<span class=\"pythonnumbercolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\">1</span><br></div><a target=\"_blank\" class=\"w3-btn w3-margin-bottom\" href=\"/learn-python/56/try-it/demo_while_break\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(76, 175, 80); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: none; display: inline-block; padding: 6px 18px; vertical-align: middle; overflow: hidden; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; text-wrap: nowrap; user-select: none; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 17px; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 16px !important;\">Try it Yourself </a></div><div><h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 32px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">The continue Statement</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 1.2em; margin-bottom: 1.2em; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">With the&nbsp;<span class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 15.75px; color: crimson; background-color: rgba(222, 222, 222, 0.3); padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px;\">continue</span>&nbsp;statement we can stop the current iteration, and continue with the next:</p><div class=\"w3-example\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(231, 233, 235); border-radius: 5px; padding: 8px 20px; margin: 24px -20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-shadow: none !important;\"><h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">Example</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\">Continue to the next iteration if i is 3:</p><div class=\"w3-code notranslate pythonHigh\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; width: auto; background-color: rgb(21, 32, 43); color: white; padding: 8px 12px; border-left: 4px solid rgb(40, 44, 52); overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 16px !important; margin-bottom: 16px !important;\"><span class=\"pythoncolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: black;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">i =&nbsp;</span><span class=\"pythonnumbercolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\">0</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"pythonkeywordcolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">while</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;i &lt;&nbsp;</span><span class=\"pythonnumbercolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\">6</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">:</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"pythonnumbercolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;i +=&nbsp;</span><span class=\"pythonnumbercolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\">1</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class=\"pythonkeywordcolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">if</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;i ==&nbsp;</span><span class=\"pythonnumbercolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\">3</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">:</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class=\"pythonkeywordcolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">continue</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class=\"pythonkeywordcolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">print</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">(i)</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><span class=\"pythonnumbercolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\"></span></span></div><a target=\"_blank\" class=\"w3-btn w3-margin-bottom\" href=\"/learn-python/56/try-it/demo_while_continue\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(76, 175, 80); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: none; display: inline-block; padding: 6px 18px; vertical-align: middle; overflow: hidden; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; text-wrap: nowrap; user-select: none; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 17px; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 16px !important;\">Try it Yourself </a></div><h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 32px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">The else Statement</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 1.2em; margin-bottom: 1.2em; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">With the&nbsp;<span class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 15.75px; color: crimson; background-color: rgba(222, 222, 222, 0.3); padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px;\">else</span>&nbsp;statement we can run a block of code once when the condition no longer is true:</p><div class=\"w3-example\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(231, 233, 235); border-radius: 5px; padding: 8px 20px; margin: 24px -20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-shadow: none !important;\"><h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">Example</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\">Print a message once the condition is false:</p><div class=\"w3-code notranslate pythonHigh\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; width: auto; background-color: rgb(21, 32, 43); color: white; padding: 8px 12px; border-left: 4px solid rgb(40, 44, 52); overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 16px !important; margin-bottom: 16px !important;\"><span class=\"pythoncolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: black;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">i =&nbsp;</span><span class=\"pythonnumbercolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\">1</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"pythonkeywordcolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">while</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;i &lt;&nbsp;</span><span class=\"pythonnumbercolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\">6</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">:</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"pythonnumbercolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class=\"pythonkeywordcolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">print</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">(i)</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"pythonnumbercolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;i +=&nbsp;</span><span class=\"pythonnumbercolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\">1</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"pythonkeywordcolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">else</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">:</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class=\"pythonkeywordcolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">print</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">(</span><span class=\"pythonstringcolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\">\"i is no longer less than 6\"</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">)</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><span class=\"pythonnumbercolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\"></span></span></div><a target=\"_blank\" class=\"w3-btn w3-margin-bottom\" href=\"/learn-python/56/try-it/demo_while_else\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(76, 175, 80); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: none; display: inline-block; padding: 6px 18px; vertical-align: middle; overflow: hidden; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; text-wrap: nowrap; user-select: none; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 17px; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 16px !important;\">Try it Yourself </a></div></div>', '0', 0, 0, '2023-06-15 01:57:12.000000', '2023-10-12 19:31:35.446447');
INSERT INTO `questions_learn` (`id`, `title`, `slug`, `description`, `codes`, `search_count`, `is_input_required`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(58, 'Python For Loops', 'python-for-loops', '<h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 32px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Python For Loops</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 1.2em; margin-bottom: 1.2em; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">A&nbsp;<span class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 15.75px; color: crimson; background-color: rgba(222, 222, 222, 0.3); padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px;\">for</span>&nbsp;loop is used for iterating over a sequence (that is either a list, a tuple, a dictionary, a set, or a string).</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 1.2em; margin-bottom: 1.2em; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">This is less like the&nbsp;<span class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 15.75px; color: crimson; background-color: rgba(222, 222, 222, 0.3); padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px;\">for</span>&nbsp;keyword in other programming languages, and works more like an iterator method as found in other object-orientated programming languages.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 1.2em; margin-bottom: 1.2em; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">With the&nbsp;<span class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 15.75px; color: crimson; background-color: rgba(222, 222, 222, 0.3); padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px;\">for</span>&nbsp;loop we can execute a set of statements, once for each item in a list, tuple, set etc.</p><div class=\"w3-example\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(231, 233, 235); border-radius: 5px; padding: 8px 20px; margin: 24px -20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-shadow: none !important;\"><h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">Example<br></h3><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\">Print each fruit in a fruit list:</p><div class=\"w3-code notranslate pythonHigh\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; width: auto; background-color: rgb(21, 32, 43); color: white; padding: 8px 12px; border-left: 4px solid rgb(40, 44, 52); overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 16px !important; margin-bottom: 16px !important;\">fruits = [<span class=\"pythonstringcolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\">\"apple\"</span>,&nbsp;<span class=\"pythonstringcolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\">\"banana\"</span>,&nbsp;<span class=\"pythonstringcolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\">\"cherry\"</span>]<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><span class=\"pythonkeywordcolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">for</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"pythonnumbercolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\"></span>x&nbsp;<span class=\"pythonkeywordcolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">in</span>&nbsp;fruits:<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><span class=\"pythonnumbercolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\"></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"pythonkeywordcolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">print</span>(x)<br></div><a target=\"_blank\" class=\"w3-btn w3-margin-bottom\" href=\"/learn-python/57/try-it/demo_for\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(76, 175, 80); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: none; display: inline-block; padding: 6px 18px; vertical-align: middle; overflow: hidden; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; text-wrap: nowrap; user-select: none; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 17px; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 16px !important;\">Try it Yourself </a></div><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 1.2em; margin-bottom: 1.2em; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">The&nbsp;<span class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 15.75px; color: crimson; background-color: rgba(222, 222, 222, 0.3); padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px;\">for</span>&nbsp;loop does not require an indexing variable to set beforehand.</p><h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 32px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Looping Through a String</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 1.2em; margin-bottom: 1.2em; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">Even strings are iterable objects, they contain a sequence of characters:</p><div class=\"w3-example\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(231, 233, 235); border-radius: 5px; padding: 8px 20px; margin: 24px -20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-shadow: none !important;\"><h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">Example</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\">Loop through the letters in the word \"banana\":</p><div class=\"w3-code notranslate pythonHigh\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; width: auto; background-color: rgb(21, 32, 43); color: white; padding: 8px 12px; border-left: 4px solid rgb(40, 44, 52); overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 16px !important; margin-bottom: 16px !important;\"><span class=\"pythonkeywordcolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">for</span>&nbsp;x&nbsp;<span class=\"pythonkeywordcolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">in</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"pythonstringcolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\">\"banana\"</span>:<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"pythonkeywordcolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">print</span>(x)<br></div><a target=\"_blank\" class=\"w3-btn w3-margin-bottom\" href=\"/learn-python/57/try-it/demo_for_string1\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(76, 175, 80); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: none; display: inline-block; padding: 6px 18px; vertical-align: middle; overflow: hidden; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; text-wrap: nowrap; user-select: none; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 17px; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 16px !important;\">Try it Yourself </a></div><h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 32px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">The break Statement</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 1.2em; margin-bottom: 1.2em; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">With the&nbsp;<span class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 15.75px; color: crimson; background-color: rgba(222, 222, 222, 0.3); padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px;\">break</span>&nbsp;statement we can stop the loop before it has looped through all the items:</p><div class=\"w3-example\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(231, 233, 235); border-radius: 5px; padding: 8px 20px; margin: 24px -20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-shadow: none !important;\"><h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">Example</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\">Exit the loop when&nbsp;<code class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 15.75px; color: crimson; background-color: rgba(222, 222, 222, 0.3);\">x</code>&nbsp;is \"banana\":</p><div class=\"w3-code notranslate pythonHigh\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; width: auto; background-color: rgb(21, 32, 43); color: white; padding: 8px 12px; border-left: 4px solid rgb(40, 44, 52); overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 16px !important; margin-bottom: 16px !important;\"><span class=\"pythoncolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: black;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">fruits = [</span><span class=\"pythonstringcolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\">\"apple\"</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">,&nbsp;</span><span class=\"pythonstringcolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\">\"banana\"</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">,&nbsp;</span><span class=\"pythonstringcolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\">\"cherry\"</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">]</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"pythonkeywordcolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">for</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;x&nbsp;</span><span class=\"pythonkeywordcolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">in</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;fruits:</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class=\"pythonkeywordcolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">print</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">(x)</span><span class=\"pythonnumbercolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class=\"pythonkeywordcolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">if</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;x ==&nbsp;</span><span class=\"pythonnumbercolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span><span class=\"pythonstringcolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\">\"banana\"</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">:</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class=\"pythonkeywordcolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">break</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><span class=\"pythonnumbercolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\"></span></span></div><a target=\"_blank\" class=\"w3-btn w3-margin-bottom\" href=\"/learn-python/57/try-it/demo_for_break\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(76, 175, 80); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: none; display: inline-block; padding: 6px 18px; vertical-align: middle; overflow: hidden; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; text-wrap: nowrap; user-select: none; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 17px; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 16px !important;\">Try it Yourself </a></div><div class=\"w3-example\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(231, 233, 235); border-radius: 5px; padding: 8px 20px; margin: 24px -20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-shadow: none !important;\"><h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">Example</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 1