\"+substrs)\r\nprint(\"Strings in the said list containing a given substring:\")\r\nprint(test(strs, substrs))', 0, 0, '2023-09-04 23:08:28', '2023-09-04 17:08:28', '2023-09-04 17:08:28', 1);
